data.description: Get ready to make new memories in this classic 4-bedroom 2 bath brick bungalow! This home boasts beautiful hardwood floors, modern fixtures and finishes, and lots of natural light throughout! Main lever features a spacious floor plan in the living room, dining room and kitchen. The recently renovated kitchen has shaker cabinets, granite countertops. Main level also has 2 bedrooms, a full bath, and an enclosed back porch-----perfect for family gatherings and entertaining guest! Finished Basement has a 3rd and 4th bedroom with walk-in closets, full bath with a jacuzzi tub and a laundry area---ideal for relative living! There is also an unfinished attic with lots of possibilities. Exterior has fenced backyard and a detached 2-car garage. Located near local transportation, expressways, stores, schools, and restaurant. Schedule your private tour today!
